FBIS3-48988 "dreeu001_r_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 ROMANIA EC, Russian Effort To Save Ilascu Praised AU3012152293 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 1400 GMT 30 Dec 93 AU3012152293 Bucharest Radio Romania Network Language: Romanian Article Type:BFN [Text] We have received the following communique from the Ministry of Foreign Affairs: The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Romania was pleased to learn about the joint declaration of the European Union and the Russian Federation addressed to the Tiraspol authorities, intended to save the life of Ion Ilascu and the urgent transferring of the members of the Ilascu group to a legally established court of the Republic of Moldova, which can ensure a fair trial, on the basis of internationally accepted juridical norms. [passage indistinct]
